@startuml
actor User
participant "MessagePage" as MP
participant "MessageService" as MS
participant "Supabase" as SB
participant "Database" as DB

User -> MP: メッセージ入力・送信ボタン押下
MP -> MS: sendMessage({ ... })
MS -> SB: messagesテーブルにinsert
SB -> DB: 書き込み処理
DB --> SB: 書き込み結果
SB --> MS: 処理結果
MS --> MP: 成功 or 失敗
MP --> User: UI更新（メッセージ表示）
@enduml